==私人生活==
懷特格拉茲從出生開始就是素食者，在15歲時更是決定成為[[純素食主義|純素食主義者]]，與捍衛人權、動物權益和自然環境的行動主義者。<ref name="#1"/>

她因為積極呼籲抵制對加拿大海豹的獵捕行為而獲得[[PETA|PETA]]的年度動物解放獎（Libby Awards）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/the-agonist-frontwoman-snags-peta2-award/ |title=THE AGONIST Frontwoman Snags PETA2 Award |publisher=Blabbermouth |date=January 30, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://noisecreep.com/the-agonists-alissa-white-gluz-stars-in-peta-ad-seal-slaughter/ |title=The Agonist’s Alissa White-Gluz Stars in PETA Ad Denouncing Seal Slaughter |publisher=Noise Creep |date=March 28, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.noisecreep.com/2011/10/03/the-agonist-alissa-white-gluz-peta2-interview/ |title=The Agonist’s Alissa White-Gluz on Being Vegan and Her Work With peta2 |publisher=Noise Creep |date=October 3, 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/arch-enemys-alissa-white-gluz-discusses-animal-rights-being-vegan-in-new-video-interview/ |title=ARCH ENEMY's ALISSA WHITE-GLUZ Discusses Animal Rights, Being Vegan In New Video Interview |publisher=Blabbermouth |date=June 24, 2014}}</ref>

她目前正與前龐克樂團Misfits的吉他手Doyle Wolfgang von Frankenstein交往。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/doyle-on-his-favorite-lady-arch-enemy-singer-alissa-white-gluz-nobody-can-out-beast-her/ |title=DOYLE On His 'Favorite Lady,' ARCH ENEMY Singer ALISSA WHITE-GLUZ: 'Nobody Can Out-Beast Her' |publisher=Blabbermouth |date=June 10, 2014}}</ref>

